==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*φύσις / phusis / foo'-sis

===Etymology===
From [[φύω]]; growth (by germination or expansion), that is, (by implication) natural production (lineal descent); by extension a genus or sort; figuratively native disposition, constitution or usage: 

===Noun===
'''φύσις'''

# ([man-]) [[kind]], [[nature]] ([-al]).

